CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: CNFinance Holdings Ltd is an equity loan service provider. It focuses on the development of small and micro-enterprises. The company generates its revenue in the form of interest and financing service fees on loans and interest on deposits with banks. Its primary target borrower segment is MSE owners who own real properties in Tier 1 and Tier 2 cities in China.
